# Core Development Rules

- **TDD Strictness**: Write tests first for new features
- **Plan First**: Always understand existing code before making changes
- **No Guesswork**: Read files before editing, never assume content
- **Run Tests**: After any change, run the relevant test suite
- **Keep It Simple**: Don't over-engineer, no speculative features
